For debouncing on client and updating URL query param. In Qwik, I can use a useSignal for the input value and useTask$/useVisibleTask$ to debounce, then use `useNavigate` or location API to update the URL. Actually updating the URL query param will trigger the routeLoader to re-run on the server (via SPA navigation). 

